{"tid":1232607,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"基於近日警察的英勇行為 應該檢討一下警察薪津福利","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T13:39:46.000Z","uid":49813,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75da0ed4fcd745d2f44eb7fe57fc80af38709876","tid":1232607,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"根據香港警務處網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/15_recruit/salary.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F15_recruit%2Fsalary.html&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPqNFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=8718dcf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/15_recruit/salary.html</a><br />\n先睇睇督察/高級督察薪酬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學位及綜合招聘考試『中文運用』和『英文運用』試卷合格(一級或以上)或同等學歷<br />\n    - 45,305元 至 84,250元 *<br />\n學位/副學士學位/高級文憑/文憑或同等學歷<br />\n    - 43,980元 至 84,250元 *<br />\n預科畢業/&ldquo;中學文憑五科3級&rdquo;或同等學歷<br />\n    - 42,665元 至 84,250元 *<br />\n<br />\n原來五科3做督察可以有4皮幾<br />\n哇 足足係入息中位數2倍幾啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁少點襯得起警察勇武既形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地一齊再睇睇警員薪酬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n    香港中學會考五科合格或以上成績，當中可包括[中國語文科及英國語文科]，或任何五個香港中學文憑科目成績[包括﹕新高中科目第2級成績，應用學習科目「達標」成績(應用學習科目最多計算兩科)，其他語言科目E級成績]，或同等學歷<br />\n    - 24,110元 至 38,580元 **<br />\n<br />\n係2萬4啊 你無聽錯我無講錯 係2萬4<br />\n只要你讀完毅進 就可以月入高過入息中位數30%<br />\n咁點得啊明明佢地英文好到可能只係唔識個press字點解姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔單止咁<br />\n我地應該要檢討下警察房屋福利<br />\n<br />\n警務人員房屋福利包括警察部門宿舍、公務員房屋福利及其他有關的房屋福利，包括：<br />\n<br />\n    本地督察級宿舍<br />\n    初級警務人員宿舍<br />\n    為職位需要而設的宿舍<br />\n    為行動需要而設的宿舍<br />\n    公務員公屋配額<br />\n    非實報實銷現金津貼<br />\n    購屋貸款計劃<br />\n    居所資助計劃<br />\n<br />\n用納稅人錢幫警察上樓係天經地義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再睇下人地D宿舍有幾大:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/732/chi/p03.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F732%2Fchi%2Fp03.htm&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPqNFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=0975deff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/732/chi/p03.htm</a><br />\n 西九龍宿舍資料<br />\n面積：八十五平方米（「E」級），七十平方米（「F」級），五十五平方米（「G」級）<br />\n車位數目：一百零九個私家車位及十二個電單車位<br />\n<br />\n秀茂坪宿舍資料<br />\n面積：七十平方米（「F」級），五十五平方米（「G」級）<br />\n車位數目：一百二十六個私家車位及十二個電單車位<br />\n<br />\n其他我就搵唔到<br />\n但原來閒閒地都55平方米 大約600呎<br />\n哇 點得啊 你當人地狗咩 咁細成間狗籠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要求大家關注下警察薪津福利 希望立會可以提出檢討</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ad0b64ad5719670910286d5fab1c2747f15a0d","tid":1232607,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5170ad43d59dc500dd7ed3d3d84859200268a446","tid":1232607,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16ad0b64ad5719670910286d5fab1c2747f15a0d","tid":1232607,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:55:00.000Z","