4%8F%E5%BA%A6%E7%BA%8C-%E5%8C%85%E5%B0%BE-%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E9%9A%8A%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98</a><br />\n<br />\n上年市民評警察appraisal咁高 唔怪得加6.5%啦想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aee5ded2baf9ea064a3890e31a8c9b17f98a94","tid":1232607,"uid":49813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警隊5年來累計增加2,377個職位，增幅約7%</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180301/20318870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180301%2F20318870&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPqNFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=45b0f7d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180301%2F20318870&h=064871c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180301/20318870</a><br />\n<br />\n2,377個 唔怪得警察咁聲勢浩蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9025cbbc16fd86ea67983bff99fd3b665444521d","tid":1232607,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"咁撚愛國 愛港<br />\n<br />\n全部減薪一半 幫國家打貿易戰就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad74f04c76475a19d3e4702ec0a4d1ebcf5d4a0","tid":1232607,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q